{"tid":1660474,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"同警犬一樣身為紀律部隊嘅你哋 覺唔覺得好唔公平","createTime":"2019-10-17T13:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T14:31:22.000Z","uid":107536,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"53d0df262660ed1a87d055e3a4c9b97176d7ac8b","tid":1660474,"uid":107536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:53:44.000Z","msg":"班警犬 成日唔洗做 又唔洗讀書 又與市民為敵 名聲又咁差<br />\n但係佢哋人工竟然係六大紀律部隊之首 仲要福利好 被港共保護<br />\n遲啲可能仲可以大幅度加人工<br />\n而作為其他紀律部隊嘅你哋 工作量又多 讀書又多過佢哋 名聲又好過佢哋 <br />\n仲要依家好有可能做埋佢地隻狗 聽佢哋指揮<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SoapboxStand/videos/1347341472093683?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSoapboxStand%2Fvideos%2F1347341472093683%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=393044e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SoapboxStand/videos/1347341472093683?sfns=mo</a><br />\n睇下巴黎啲消防員 點樣表達不滿同反抗<br />\n<br />\n有無可能舉行一個除左警犬之外嘅紀律部隊大型集會 表達各紀律部隊人員嘅不滿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca063feb2e527365cc265440e5c62e8859cc15da","tid":1660474,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"48a4dbaf6b2abafa85846b46db4351410219e82d","tid":1660474,"uid":107536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"1/10推<br />\n<br />\n1020見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48258ed7a56a4c64177b5ef6a88b0d1965ceaf7b","tid":1660474,"uid":107536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:56:58.000Z","msg":"2/10推<br />\n<br />\n1020見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507a3770cccdc96a046